main_text: Mobile Point of Sale (mPoS) systems empower businesses to process transactions efficiently anywhere in-store or at remote locations, improving service speed and customer satisfaction. With the global shift to cashless payments, mPoS systems accommodate various payment types, including cards and mobile wallets, catering to diverse preferences.

This highly integrated and secure mPoS terminal design supports both contact and contactless payments via Near Field Communication (NFC). It incorporates wireless connectivity, drives transaction receipts printing, and operates on low power to extend usage time. Additionally, enhanced security features such as anti-tamper, secure boot, and authentication ensure secure transactions, boosting business reliability.
benefits: Seamless wireless operation with Wi-Fi and BluetoothÂ®Low Energy (LE) enables cordless use for flexible and convenient terminal placement.
Dual card reader supports chip and NFC cards, enhancing convenience and speeding up checkout.
Advanced security functions for anti-tamper detection, secure boot, and secure authentication provide robust protection and reliability.
Battery-operated design supports USB-C and Qi-compatible wireless charging, offering versatile power options.
Operates at 15W, with an option for 100W to meet higher power needs.
